    <item>
      <title>小狐狸的热心帮助 —— 善良与助人</title>
      <link>https://blog.jaxiu.cn/blog/2026-03/%E5%B0%8F%E7%8B%90%E7%8B%B8%E7%9A%84%E7%83%AD%E5%BF%83%E5%B8%AE%E5%8A%A9-%E5%96%84%E8%89%AF%E4%B8%8E%E5%8A%A9%E4%BA%BA/</link>
